 R←APLVersion sel
⍝ returns elements of APLVersion specified by sel (see below)
⍝ passing any other than the supported value simply returns the full APLVersion string
 R←'.'⎕WG'APLVersion'
 :Select sel
 :Case 1   ⍝ sel=1: return leading 3 characters of lowercase platform name
     R←⎕C 3↑1⊃R
 :Case 2   ⍝ sel=2: return major version no.
     R←2 1⊃'.'⎕VFI 2⊃R
 :EndSelect
